Package ca.mcgill.ecse211.ziplineproject

Class TestNavigation

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse211.ziplineproject.TestNavigation

  • public class TestNavigation
extends java.lang.Object
    Test the Navigation class The robot is instructed to perform the equivalent of the following pseudocode: 
    

    Wait for button press
    for i in range (0,4):   
        Go forward for 2 tiles
        Turn right by 90o
    Go forward for 2 tiles
    Turn right by 153.435o
    Go forward for 2.236 tiles
    Turn left by 108.435o
    Go forward for 1.414 tiles
    Turn left by 45o
    Stop
    This is a picture of the robot's trajectory. The starting coordinate is (1,1), which is the red dot.
    Author:
    Younes Boubekeur
